snippet: A Milwaukee man took his own life after inadvertently killing his teenage nephew in connection with a traffic accident that killed a younger nephew.
abstract: Ricky Chiles III commits suicide after inadvertently killing his teenage nephew Rasheed Chiles in connection with traffic accident that killed his younger nephew; Chiles had also killed Archie Brown, who was involved in accident.
lead_paragraph: A Milwaukee man took his own life after inadvertently killing his teenage nephew in connection with a traffic accident that killed a younger nephew.

headline.main: Wisconsin: String of Deaths Continues With Suspect’s Suicide
